ENTRY            A0375   20260127   20260327   20260327       A130
SUBENT        A0375001   20260127   20260327   20260327       A130
BIB                 13         30
TITLE      Direct measurement of the absolute cross section of
            p(7Be,gamma)8B
AUTHOR     (F.Terrasi, L.Gialanella, G.Imbriani, F.Strieder,
           L.Campajola, A.D'Onofrio, U.Greife, G.Gyurky,
           C.Lubritto, A.Ordine, V.Roca, C.Rolfs, M.Romano,
           D.Rogalla, C.Sabbarese, E.Somorjai, H.P.Trautvetter)
REFERENCE  (J,NP/A,688,539,2001)
           #doi:10.1016/S0375-9474(01)00781-3
FACILITY   (VDGT,2ITYNAP) 3 mega-volts tandem
INSTITUTE  (2ITYFSN,2ITYNAP,2GERBOC,1USACSM,3HUNDEB)
           (2ITYITY) Astronomical Observatory of Capodimonte,
            Napoli
SAMPLE     Hydrogen gas target with an effective
           length = 376+/-8 mm.
MONITOR    (18-AR-0(3-LI-7,EL)18-AR-0,,DA)
METHOD     (EXTB) 4+ charge state of 7Be and an average intensity
           of 30 pA.
           (SITA,MOMIX)
REL-REF    (A,A0414002,F.Strieder+,J,NP/A,696,219,2001)
DETECTOR   (SIBAR) Four collimated detectors placed at 30, +45,
           -45 and 60 degrees with respect to the beam axis
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information about source of uncertainty
STATUS     (TABLE,,F.Terrasi+,J,NP/A,688,539,2001) Tables were
           received from G.Imbriani. Data presented on fig. 1.
HISTORY    (20020706C)
           (20020628R) From G.Imbriani
           (20021217U) Last checking has been done.
           (20160708A) Major revision was done in Sub 004.
           (20260127A) SD: Corrections in all Subents.
           ERR-T -> DATA-ERR.
ENDBIB              30
COMMON               1          3
EN-ERR
KEV
        0.5
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           37
SUBENT        A0375002   20260127   20260327   20260327       A130
BIB                  2          6
REACTION   ((1-H-1(3-LI-7,EL)1-H-1,,DA,,RTH)=
           (3-LI-7(P,EL)3-LI-7,,DA,,RTH))
HISTORY    (20260127A) SD: SF7=P deleted from REACTION code.
           Right part of reaction code was added. Col. MISC
           deleted. EN -> EN-CM (value was taken from col. MISC).
           ERR-T -> DATA-ERR.
ENDBIB               6
COMMON               2          3
EN-CM      DATA-ERR
KEV        NO-DIM
       975.       0.03
ENDCOMMON            3
DATA                 2          3
ANG-CM     DATA
ADEG       NO-DIM
        60.       2.45
        90.       1.31
       120.       1.01
ENDDATA              5
ENDSUBENT           20
SUBENT        A0375003   20260127   20260327   20260327       A130
BIB                  2          6
REACTION   ((1-H-1(4-BE-7,EL)1-H-1,,DA,,RTH)=
           (4-BE-7(P,EL)4-BE-7,,DA,,RTH))
HISTORY    (20260127A) SD: SF7=P deleted from REACTION code.
           Right part of reaction code was added. Col. MISC
           deleted. EN -> EN-CM (value was taken from col. MISC).
           ERR-T -> DATA-ERR.
ENDBIB               6
COMMON               1          3
EN-CM
KEV
      954.
ENDCOMMON            3
DATA                 3          3
ANG-CM     DATA       DATA-ERR
ADEG       NO-DIM     NO-DIM
        60.       0.81       0.12
        90.       1.01       0.09
       120.       1.42       0.11
ENDDATA              5
ENDSUBENT           20
SUBENT        A0375004   20260127   20260327   20260327       A130
BIB                  3          8
REACTION  R((1-H-1(4-BE-7,G)5-B-8,,SIG)=(4-BE-7(P,G)5-B-8,,SIG))
          S((1-H-1(4-BE-7,G)5-B-8,,SIG,,SFC)=
           (4-BE-7(P,G)5-B-8,,SIG,,SFC))
COMMENT    - By compiler: statistical error is main source of
           datum uncertainty.
HISTORY    (20160708A) EN was replaced by EN-CM, MISC was deleted.
           (20260127A) SD: PART-DET and STATUS deleted.
           ERR-T -> DATA-ERR.
ENDBIB               8
NOCOMMON             0          0
DATA                 5          1
EN-CM      DATA      RDATA-ERR  RDATA      SDATA-ERR  S
KEV        MICRO-B    MICRO-B    B*EV       B*EV
       990.       0.40       0.12       16.5        4.8
